{"tid":1630344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：公眾活動中4人送院　一男一女情況嚴重","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:18:30.000Z","uid":20916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e036be38c0c3fd5f9c137cf3d7df000c316d6e","tid":1630344,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"醫管局表示，截至晚上7時，在公眾活動中有4人需要送院，律敦治醫院的1名男傷者、瑪嘉烈醫院的1男1女傷者，情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一名送往廣華醫院的男傷者，已經出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484625-20191006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484625-20191006.htm&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6jUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=b7143e1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484625-20191006.htm&h=2bde2c5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484625-20191006.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8dc42e795276e171246f8666efae09adc7029962","tid":1630344,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9517e066d33e83391b09c2c5ce026ec490d63ad","tid":1630344,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e4b6cb453826f988924221188d73ff662252b0","tid":1630344,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"女應該係斷腳"},{"pid":"06f38749ef74d3d72519deabd21570eb01717b22","tid":1630344,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"！唔該小心你屋企樓下個看更！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecd2d9891369fd944eaf22b557d731ad9bad1cd9","tid":1630344,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"得4個有得送院..."},{"pid":"e527a2bfd8358031c557f7c7c38c9da27c695b26","tid":1630344,"uid":295549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"送廣華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a21d1774f6ecf8bce019c37629e6ff51a76099a","tid":1630344,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4e4b6cb453826f988924221188d73ff662252b0","tid":1630344,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"女應該係斷腳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"咁男會唔會係的士佬"},{"pid":"5465c7eb881069d70f2ac2de546fe229ddafde70","tid":1630344,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a21d1774f6ecf8bce019c37629e6ff51a76099a","tid":1630344,"uid":20916,"like":0,"d